      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a great project or a dependable work horse for someone willing to put in a little effort. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scuffs, faded paint on the hood, and a few minor dings consistent with regular use. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear on the driver's seat, though all essential electronics remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in peak operating shape.",
