    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone who prioritizes function over aesthetics. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and a few stains, though the cabin remains comfortable and smoke-free. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it will eventually need attention for a slow oil leak and aging suspension components. It\u2019s an honest car that has been maintained enough to stay on the road, perfect for a commuter or a first-time owner.",
