      "description": "Looking for your next great project? This vehicle is ready for someone with a vision! While it's in poor condition and will definitely need some mechanical and cosmetic TLC to get back to its best, it offers a fantastic opportunity for a DIY enthusiast or anyone looking for a budget-friendly fixer-upper. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own!",
