    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm finally parting with my pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is an absolute dream. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014always garage-kept and hand-washed every Sunday. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape; you\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a single blemish, though if you look really close at the rear bumper, there's a tiny mark that only I seem to notice. It drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019m looking for a fellow enthusiast who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come by, grab a coffee, and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
